title: Fairy Tail OST Collection - Complete as of 6th July 2015
description:
Complete OST collection for Fairy Tail up to Episode 243. (Seasons 1 - 7 of the anime.)
Contains OST Volumes 1-5 (Vol 4 & 5 are 2 disc sets)
OST for Fairy Tail Houou no Miko (aka Fairy Tail the Movie: The Phoenix Princess)
All character songs 
All opening songs, all ending songs.

Good quality.  OST Volumes 1-5 have cover art.

This is an updated version of the Torrent available here (https://thepiratebay.vg/torrent/11159842/Fairy_Tail_OST_Collection_-_Complete), and now includes the Fairy Tail Original Sound Collection (OST Vol 5.) that was released on May 13 2015
